WEBVTT

00:06.380 --> 00:07.650
<i>[Bat Lady]</i>
<i>Previously on</i> Shelter...

00:07.850 --> 00:10.240
[Spoon] Dylan Shakes,
missing kid from Kasselton.

00:10.440 --> 00:12.490
Ashley Kent,
missing kid from Kasselton.

00:12.690 --> 00:13.780
What does one have to do
with the other?

00:13.980 --> 00:16.580
Mrs. Kent, your daughter,
Ashley, is she okay?

00:16.780 --> 00:18.830
We lost Ashley,
but I will find her.

00:19.030 --> 00:20.330
[gunshot]

00:20.530 --> 00:22.170
[Bat Lady] You've done enough.

00:22.370 --> 00:25.880
Is this where you buried him?

00:26.080 --> 00:27.510
<i>[Mickey] We think</i>
<i>whoever did this</i>

00:27.710 --> 00:28.510
<i>kidnapped our friend.</i>

00:28.710 --> 00:30.470
We have no idea
where Ashley is.

00:30.670 --> 00:32.180
Okay, look, I'm gonna tell you
what I told the police,

00:32.380 --> 00:33.430
and then I want you gone.

00:33.630 --> 00:34.510
<i>The man who did this</i>
<i>to my husband,</i>

00:34.710 --> 00:35.680
<i>he had a tattoo on his face.</i>

00:35.880 --> 00:36.970
[Octoface] That doesn't belong
to you.

00:37.170 --> 00:38.350
<i>[Mrs. Kent] An octopus.</i>

00:38.550 --> 00:39.690
[Octoface] Stop right there!

00:39.890 --> 00:41.020
- [gasps]
- [cheers and applause]

00:41.220 --> 00:43.940
This year's musical is
<i>Phantom of the Opera.</i>

00:44.140 --> 00:45.860
I'm gonna destroy his world.

00:46.060 --> 00:47.990
[crowd chanting] Buck, Buck,
Buck, Buck, Buck, Buck!

00:48.190 --> 00:49.490
[Ellen] Surprise.

00:49.690 --> 00:51.410
<i>[Troy] Didn't you have, like,</i>
<i>a thing with my dad?</i>

00:51.610 --> 00:53.240
In fact, we were a thing.

00:53.440 --> 00:55.080
And you were friends
with my mom.

00:55.280 --> 00:56.540
Best friends.

00:56.740 --> 00:58.000
<i>[Troy] You're not answering</i>
<i>my texts.</i>

00:58.200 --> 00:59.460
<i>You're ignoring me at school.</i>
<i>What's your deal?</i>

00:59.660 --> 01:00.710
I can't believe
I could even talk...

01:00.910 --> 01:02.670
- I was joking.
- Get the fuck away from me!

01:02.870 --> 01:04.790
- Guys.
- [Spoon] Oh, they clearly knew

01:04.990 --> 01:06.670
the combination
to Ashley's locker.

01:06.870 --> 01:09.880
Oh, my God.
Mickey is gonna shit.

01:10.080 --> 01:11.550
You're Lizzy Sobek.

01:11.750 --> 01:12.800
[dramatic music]

01:13.000 --> 01:15.650
You said my dad is still alive.

01:23.200 --> 01:26.110
[tense music]

01:26.310 --> 01:32.960
♪ ♪

01:40.510 --> 01:43.420
[sirens wailing]

01:43.620 --> 01:46.980
<i>[indistinct whispering]</i>

01:55.690 --> 01:58.600
<i>[indistinct radio chatter]</i>

01:58.800 --> 02:01.600
[sirens wailing]

02:01.800 --> 02:08.460
♪ ♪

02:22.890 --> 02:24.310
Holy shit.

02:25.600 --> 02:26.710
Dad.

02:26.910 --> 02:33.820
♪ ♪

02:37.070 --> 02:39.970
[♪ Ned's Atomic Dustbin:
"Until You Find Out"]

02:40.170 --> 02:42.980
[breathing heavily]

02:43.180 --> 02:46.690
[intense rock music]

02:46.890 --> 02:49.610
<i>[singer] ♪ All you need do</i>
<i>is catch me ♪</i>

02:49.810 --> 02:51.480
