11:09.390 --> 11:12.070
[Ken retching]

11:12.270 --> 11:13.320
All right, babe.

11:13.520 --> 11:15.320
Why don't we take this
to the bathroom, hmm?

11:15.520 --> 11:17.410
- Wanna make out there?
- [Shira] Yeah.

11:17.610 --> 11:19.370
Ken, you smell like ass.

11:19.570 --> 11:21.160
