- That was spot-on. Uncanny.

11:24.070 --> 11:25.790
[retching]

11:25.990 --> 11:27.460
[both laugh]

11:27.660 --> 11:29.460
- He is such a dumbass.
- Ugh.

11:29.660 --> 11:30.750
Why are you dating him, again?

11:30.950 --> 11:33.550
Because he's a hot dumbass.

11:33.750 --> 11:34.880
- No.
- Yeah.

11:35.080 --> 11:37.720
- No.
- [both laugh]

11:37.920 --> 11:40.930
<i>[announcer] And here it comes,</i>
<i>the last song of the night.</i>

11:41.130 --> 11:43.890
Well, since your date got
swiped by whiskey

11:44.090 --> 11:46.480
and mine didn't make it
past the parking lot...

11:46.680 --> 11:48.480
<i>[singer] ♪ You sweet thing ♪</i>

11:48.680 --> 11:50.650
[♪ The Flys:
"Got You (Where I Want You)"]

11:50.850 --> 11:52.110
...may I have this dance?

11:52.310 --> 11:53.570
- Of course, madam.
- [both laugh]

11:53.770 --> 11:54.650
Right this way. Right this way.

11:54.850 --> 11:57.650
- Oh, thank you.
- [both laugh]

11:57.850 --> 12:00.030
♪ ♪

12:00.230 --> 12:04.750
<i>[singer]</i>
<i>♪ Got you where I want you ♪</i>

12:04.950 --> 12:07.210
<i>♪ Yeah ♪</i>

12:07.410 --> 12:10.080
<i>♪ Ah-ooh ♪</i>

12:10.280 --> 12:12.710
I'm gonna miss you
so fucking much next year.

12:12.910 --> 12:17.260
<i>[singer]</i>
<i>♪ Got you where I want you ♪</i>

12:17.460 --> 12:20.760
<i>♪ Yeah ♪</i>

12:20.960 --> 12:25.430
<i>♪ Hey ♪</i>

12:25.630 --> 12:28.310
<i>♪ Maybe just a smile ♪</i>

12:28.510 --> 12:30.230
♪ ♪

12:30.430 --> 12:32.360
Gay!

12:32.560 --> 12:33.900
Don't stop. You're hot.

12:34.100 --> 12:36.360
<i>- [singer] ♪ Oh, hey ♪</i>
- [both laugh]

12:36.560 --> 12:38.900
<i>♪ Did you know</i>
<i>that I can dance? ♪</i>

12:39.100 --> 12:43.200
<i>♪ Could we talk for a while? ♪</i>

12:43.400 --> 12:45.700
Do you wanna get out of here?

12:45.900 --> 12:47.870
<i>[singer]</i>
<i>♪ Well, I think you're smart ♪</i>

12:48.070 --> 12:50.040
Yeah. Let's go.

12:50.240 --> 12:53.170
<i>[singer] ♪ You sweet thing ♪</i>

12:53.370 --> 12:56.420
<i>♪ Tell me your sign ♪</i>

12:56.620 --> 12:59.110
<i>♪ I'm dying here ♪</i>

13:01.110 --> 13:03.850
[Hannah] Hey. Wait up.

13:04.050 --> 13:05.760
Oh.

13:05.960 --> 13:07.180
What a speech.

13:07.380 --> 13:08.640
You know what?
That was not cool.

13:08.840 --> 13:09.890
Very inspiring.

13:10.090 --> 13:12.810
