You see those glasses?

13:30.860 --> 13:32.710
Well, I mean, they take up
half of her face.

13:32.910 --> 13:35.090
- You can't miss 'em.
- [Hannah] So the rumor is,

13:35.290 --> 13:36.460
she got a Groupon
for some Botox

13:36.660 --> 13:37.920
at a strip mall
in Staten Island.

13:38.120 --> 13:39.130
[laughing]
Stop.

13:39.330 --> 13:41.590
So she's got, like,
a serious droopy eye

13:41.790 --> 13:44.300
hiding out
under those sunglasses.

13:44.500 --> 13:47.260
Is it bad that her misfortune
is my drug?

13:47.460 --> 13:48.930
- [laughing]
- Ugh, I would never judge you.

13:49.130 --> 13:50.480
Never.

13:50.680 --> 13:54.350
Hey, uh...
what are you doing later?

13:54.550 --> 13:57.520
Um, just... just some work.

13:57.720 --> 13:59.360
[Hannah] Mm, that sounds fun.

13:59.560 --> 14:02.240
Well, I have
an alternate proposal.

14:02.440 --> 14:03.410
Okay.

